        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段造好 恒指再升186點報21603點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股開市初段繼續跟隨外圍造好，恒生指數開市報21603點，升186點或0.87%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5057點，升42點或0.85%；國企指數以8031點開市，升65點或0.82%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股普遍造好，阿里巴巴(09988)開報111.8元，升3.33%；騰訊(00700)開報464.6元，升2.34%；美團(03690)開報146.5元，升0.41%。滙控(00005)開報79元，升0.64%；友邦(01299)開報52.3元，升0.19%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230703-101723__source-web_09988-8_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230703-101723__source-web_09988-8_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">山東黃金(01787)發盈喜，該股今早開報22元，跌1.35%。中國儒意(00136)發23.41億元換股債，該股今早應聲向下，開報2.23元，跌3.46%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14855271-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e9%80%a0%e5%a5%bd-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%86%8d%e5%8d%87186%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b121603%e9%bb%9e",
